location.fullValue: Birch with Included Basement Plan, Green Ridge

data.description: Step into this delightful two-story gem boasting 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and an array of impressive upgrades including a high-efficiency furnace, central A/C, a convenient 1st-floor laundry room, and not one but two inviting porches that overlook a spacious and oversized yard. Complete with all appliances, this home is a gateway to the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Nestled just minutes away from the picturesque Shabbona Lake State Park, this haven offers unparalleled access to nature's wonders - ideal for fishing, camping, and boating enthusiasts. Although listed 'As-Is,' this property exudes excellent condition and holds immense potential for your dream lifestyle.
